  "detailed_description": "Gulu is the puzzle game with a simple rule, but it's not so easy to be solved.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou should put all squares back to their origninal positions. However, every step you move will also affect other adjacent 3 squares.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs a Rubik's cube, you can figure out some formulas that can slove all puzzles. moreover, you can just randomly shuffle them for relaxing.",
